24
00:01:29,909 --> 00:01:34,619
I mentioned earlier that mothers talk to their infants about their own desire first.

25
00:01:34,619 --> 00:01:40,299
Then, between 18 to 36 months of age, the mother talks to the infant about their thoughts

26
00:01:40,299 --> 00:01:45,390
