27
00:01:45,390 --> 00:01:48,469
After that, the mother talks about other people&#39;s mental states.

28
00:01:48,469 --> 00:01:50,430
Instead of saying things like…

29
00:01:50,430 --> 00:01:53,359
&quot;You should do this&quot;, the mother says things like…

30
00:01:53,359 --> 00:01:55,700
&quot;Daniel thinks that the dog is cute.&quot;

31
00:01:55,700 --> 00:02:00,920
Talking to infants about the thoughts and beliefs of others foster the infant’s understanding

32
